(b) Contracting officers are encouraged to insert the provision \cf3 52.201-1\cf4 , Acquisition 360: Voluntary Survey, in accordance\
with agency procedures.\
(c) Contracting officers shall not review information until after contract award and shall not consider it in the award\
decision.\

