\f0\b 3.1001 Definitions.\

\f1\b0 As used in this subpart-\

\f2\i Subcontract 
\f1\i0 means any contract entered into by a subcontractor to furnish supplies or services for performance of a prime contract or a subcontract.\

\f2\i Subcontractor 
