4.2100 Scope of subpart.\

\f1\b0 This subpart implements paragraphs (a)(1)(A) and (a)(1)(B) of section 889 of the John S. McCain National Defense Authorization Act for Fiscal Year 2019 (Pub. L. 115-232).\

\f0\b 4.2101 Definitions.\

\f1\b0 As used in this subpart\'97\

\f2\i Backhaul 
\f1\i0 means intermediate links between the core network, or backbone network, and the small subnetworks at the edge of the network (
\f2\i e.g.
\f1\i0 , connecting cell phones/towers to the core telephone network). Backhaul can be wireless (
\f2\i e.g.
\f1\i0 , microwave) or wired (
\f2\i e.g.
\f1\i0 , fiber optic, coaxial cable, Ethernet).\

\f2\i Covered foreign country 
\f1\i0 means The People\'92s Republic of China. 
