\f1\b0 (a) As required by the Small Business Act (\cf3 15 U.S.C.637(e)\cf4 ) and the Office of Federal Procurement Policy Act (\cf3 41 U.S.C.1708\cf4 ), agencies must make notices of proposed contract actions available as specified in paragraph (b) of this section.\
