\fs20 5.701 Scope.\

\f1\b0 This subpart prescribes posting requirements for presolicitation and award notices for actions funded in whole or in part by the American Recovery and Reinvestment Act of 2009 (Pub. L. 111-5) (Recovery Act). The requirements of this subpart enhance transparency to the public.\

\f0\b 5.702 Applicability.\

\f1\b0 This subpart applies to all actions expected to exceed $25,000 funded in whole or in part by the Recovery Act. Unlike subparts \cf3 5.2 \cf4 and \cf3 5.3\cf4 , this subpart includes additional requirements for orders and for actions that are not both fixed-price and competitive.\

