\fs20 7.400 Scope of subpart.\

\f1\b0 This subpart\'97\
(a) Implements section 555 of the FAA (Federal Aviation Administration) Reauthorization Act of 2018 (\cf3 Pub. L. 115-254\cf4 ); (b) Provides guidance when acquiring equipment and more than one method of acquisition is available for use; and\
