\f1\b0 If an agency is unable to satisfy requirements for supplies and services from the mandatory sources listed in \cf3 8.002 \cf4 and \cf3 8.003\cf4 , agencies are encouraged to consider satisfying requirements from or through the non-mandatory sources listed in paragraph (a) of this section (not listed in any order of priority) before considering the non-mandatory source listed in paragraph (b) of this section. When satisfying requirements from non-mandatory sources, see \cf3 7.105\cf4 (b) and \cf3 part 19 \cf4 regarding consideration of small business, veteran-owned small business, service-disabled veteran-owned small business, HUBZone small business, small disadvantaged business (including 8(a) participants), and women-owned small business concerns.\
