\fs20 9.100 Scope of subpart.\

\f1\b0 This subpart prescribes policies, standards, and procedures for determining whether prospective contractors and subcontractors are responsible.\

\f0\b 9.101 Definitions.\

\f2\i\b0 Administrative proceeding 
\f1\i0 means a non-judicial process that is adjudicatory in nature in order to make a determination of fault or liability (
