\f0\b 9.102 Applicability.\

\f1\b0 (a) This subpart applies to all proposed contracts with any prospective contractor that is located-\
(1) In the United States or its outlying areas; or\
(2) Elsewhere, unless application of the subpart would be inconsistent with the laws or customs where the contractor is\
located.\
(b) This subpart does not apply to proposed contracts with-\
(1) Foreign, State, or local governments;\
(2) Other U.S. Government agencies or their instrumentalities; or\
(3) Agencies for people who are blind or severely disabled (see \cf3 subpart 8.7\cf4 ).\

\f0\b 9.103 Policy.\

\f1\b0 (a) Purchases shall be made from, and contracts shall be awarded to, responsible prospective contractors only.\
