\f0\b 15.308 Source selection decision.\

\f1\b0 The source selection authority\'92s (SSA) decision shall be based on a comparative assessment of proposals against all\
source selection criteria in the solicitation. While the SSA may use reports and analyses prepared by others, the source selection decision shall represent the SSA\'92s independent judgment. The source selection decision shall be documented,\
