\f1\b0 (a) The contracting officer shall price the 8(a) contract in accordance with \cf3 subpart 15.4\cf4 . If required by \cf3 subpart 15.4\cf4 , the SBA shall obtain certified cost or pricing data from the 8(a) contractor. If the SBA requests audit assistance to determine the proposed price to be fair and reasonable in a sole source acquisition, the contracting activity shall furnish it to the extent it is available.\
