(2) If a project wage determination for the primary site of the work expires after bid opening but before award, the contracting officer shall request an extension of the project wage determination expiration date from the Administrator, Wage and Hour Division. The request for extension shall be supported by a written finding, which shall include a brief statement\
of factual support, that the extension is necessary and proper in the public interest to prevent injustice or undue hardship\
or to avoid serious impairment of the conduct of Government business. If necessary, the contracting officer shall delay\
