\f0\b 22.603 Applicability.\

\f1\b0 The requirements in \cf3 22.602 \cf4 apply to contracts (including for this purpose, indefinite-delivery contracts, basic ordering agreements, and blanket purchase agreements) and subcontracts under Section 8(a) of the Small Business Act, for the manufacture or furnishing of supplies that-\
