\f0\b\fs20 22.1002-4 Application of the Fair Labor Standards Act minimum wage.\

\f1\b0 No contractor or subcontractor holding a service contract for any dollar amount shall pay any of its employees working on the contract less than the minimum wage specified in section 6(a)(1) of the Fair Labor Standards Act (\cf3 29 U.S.C.206\cf4 ).\

