\fs20 22.1800 Scope.\

\f1\b0 This subpart prescribes policies and procedures requiring contractors to utilize the Department of Homeland Security (DHS), United States Citizenship and Immigration Service\'92s employment eligibility verification program (E-Verify) as the means for verifying employment eligibility of certain employees.\

\f0\b 22.1801 Definitions.\

