incurred (\cf3 subpart 16.5\cf4 ); and\
(4) The fixed-hourly rate portion of time-and-materials and labor-hours contracts and subcontracts (\cf3 subpart 16.6\cf4 ).\

\f2\i Flexibly-priced contracts and subcontracts 
